X needs to stay within the laws of the countries it operates in.  My point is: I much prefer Elon's approach of allowing stuff that is within the law, such as fake news, and fighting it with community notes, instead of outlawing whatever the government deems "fake", like the EU is planning.  Or worse: by making laws with vague guidelines but</div>
